window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"<b>***A LitRPG Progression Epic*** </b><br> <br> <b>Book 7 of Guardian of Aster Fall!</b><br> <br> In the Void beyond Aster Fall, Sam stands watch at the fortress of Silverguard, protecting the world from an ancient enemy. His strength as an Astral Titan is all that stands between it and destruction.<br> <br> Meanwhile, dimensional cracks are spreading through the World Seal, the barrier that protects Aster Fall from invasion by the Outsider galaxy. Flaws are appearing with increasing frequency as demonic armies flood through, including old enemies from the First War. If the seal fails completely, Aster Fall will break and disaster will follow. <br> <br> To save his home, Sam plans to sends his avatars into the unstable dimensions around Aster Fall to find Asenya, the World Seal's creator. Only with her help will he be able to repair it before it shatters completely.<br> <br> Primordial enchantments, crafting, and battles await in the seventh volume of this epic series!</p>"; 
